                            <div class="provocative-box">
                                <h5>5-Round Imagination Protocol</h5>
                                
                                <p><strong>Round 1:</strong> Imagine activity with fear (note symptoms)</p>
                                <p><strong>Round 2:</strong> Imagine with less fear, more neutral (note changes)</p>
                                <p><strong>Round 3:</strong> Imagine with calm confidence (note changes)</p>
                                <p><strong>Round 4:</strong> Imagine with actual enjoyment (note changes)</p>
                                <p><strong>Round 5:</strong> Imagine with joy and gratitude for your body (note changes)</p>
                                
